Chapter 4: The Matrix

The files in this directory include coding assignments from The Matrix. Some source files needed to test procedures
(e.g. text files) may not be included in this repo.

Notes:

1) The file mat.py is located in the main repo as the module is used in multiple chapters.

2) The file mat.py was provided and included the class Mat. Problem 2.14.10 required completing the unfinished
procedures in vec.py. The vec.py file can be found in the main repository

Error_Correcting.py: Lab Error-correcting codes
Transformations_2D.py: Lab Transformations in @d geometry
mat.py: Write selected procedures for Vec class (Problem 4.17.12)
Matrix_problems.py